  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The Advance® 18 PTX® Balloon Catheter study is a clinical trial to study the safety and
      effectiveness of the Advance 18® PTX® Balloon Catheter in the treatment of lesions in the
      superficial femoral artery and popliteal artery.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
